text: Ahmad Ghasemi (; born 24 April 1995) is an Iranian judoka Ahmad Ghasemi was runner-up title in the Asian Junior Championship in 2009 held in Lebanon. He participated at the 2014 Asian U21 Championships Hong Kong, winning a bronze medal. == References == == Other websites == Category:1995 births Category:Living people Category:Judoka Category:Sportspeople from Tehran
